snippet.title: The Great Ace Attorney Chronicles - Gameplay Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Courtroom chaos and intense investigations collide with two games included in The Great Ace Attorney Chronicles, coming to Nintendo Switch on July 27, 2021!

Travel back in time to late 19th century Japan and London to play as Ryunosuke Naruhodo, Phoenix Wright's ancestor, in this action-packed prequel.

Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/the-great-ace-attorney-chronicles-switch/
